Polynomials with score up to 16 are included. The score of a polynomial is

$$
\begin{align}
score&=deg(P) + \sum_{i=0}^{i\le deg(P)} \left|a_i\right| \\
P &= \sum_{i=0}^{i\le deg(P)}a_i x^i
\end{align}
$$

Only polynomials up to degree 12 are included.
